lf-care tips, smile enticing videos, UIC resources and much more).  We do the research, so you don’t have to!  The Listserv is exclusively for registered UIC students.       Sign-Up For Our Rockstar Listserv Here!      Modified on April 29, 2020                 UIC Logo        Wellness Center          Contact   Suite 238 750 S Halsted Street  Chicago, IL 60607  Phone: (312) 413-2120  wellnesscenter@uic.edu        Social Media Accounts    Facebook    Twitter    Instagram    YouTube             UIC.edu links   UIC.edu  Academic Calendar  Athletics  Campus Directory  Disability Resources  Emergency Information  Event Calendar  Job Openings  Library  Maps  UIC Safe Mobile App  UIC Today  UI Health  Veterans Affairs        Powered by Red 2.38.0  © 2020 The Board of Trustees of the University of Illinois |  Privacy Statement    Campuses   University of Illinois System  Urbana-Champaign  Springfield      Cookie Settings                 